name: DJ Four-Word-The Revolution Will NOT Be Centralized Side-A Intro

metadata.name: The Revolution Will NOT Be Centralized Side-A Intro
metadata.description:
I made this intro track for this NFT mixtape using unused portions of the original recording. 

This album is an unreleased, live recording of a DJ routine I performed in a barn house, where I had the privilege of being able to set up the decks for some scratch practice on 5/7/2016. We're all lucky to have been able to capture this routine on recording! Truly a memorable night that could never be forgotten!
